http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: This file contains the CGI Earth Resource Environmental Impact vocabulary, as defined by the IUGS Commission for Geoscience Information (CGI) Geoscience Terminology Working Group. The vocabulary defines concepts for categorizing impacts associated with Earth Resource extraction activities. By extension, this vocabulary includes all concepts in this conceptScheme, as well as concepts in any previous versions of the scheme.
